casebody.data:
Salvatore MORETTI, Petitioner
v.
Michael MORDAGA No. 19-5496 Supreme Court of the United States. October 7, 2019

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and the petition for a writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Justice Alito took no part in the consideration or decision of this motion and this petition.
